                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voici la nuit : je vais ensevelir mes morts,\nLes songes, les désirs, les douceurs, les remords,\nTout le passé… Je vais ensevelir mes morts."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Je cacherai, parmi les sombres violettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Ton visage d’amie aux tendresses muettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Ô toi qui dors parmi les sombres violettes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je cacherai, parmi les sombres violettes,\nTon visage d’amie aux tendresses muettes,\nÔ toi qui dors parmi les sombres violettes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Je pleurerai l’étoile éteinte du regard…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Dans l’effort de la vie et les heurts du hasard,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Je pleurerai l’étoile éteinte du regard…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je pleurerai l’étoile éteinte du regard…\nDans l’effort de la vie et les heurts du hasard,\nJe pleurerai l’étoile éteinte du regard…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Je couvrirai d’encens, de roses et de roses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "La pâle chevelure et les paupières closes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "D’un amour dont l’ardeur mourut parmi les roses.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je couvrirai d’encens, de roses et de roses,\nLa pâle chevelure et les paupières closes\nD’un amour dont l’ardeur mourut parmi les roses."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Je sentirai monter vers moi l’odeur des morts,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Abolissant en moi les craintes, les remords,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et m’apportant l’esprit indifférent des morts.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je sentirai monter vers moi l’odeur des morts,\nAbolissant en moi les craintes, les remords,\nEt m’apportant l’esprit indifférent des morts."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Je trouverai, sous les grappes de violettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6−6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Les sanglots apaisés et les larmes muettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Sous les fleurs de la mort, les sombres violettes…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je trouverai, sous les grappes de violettes,\nLes sanglots apaisés et les larmes muettes,\nSous les fleurs de la mort, les sombres violettes…"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Déjà, se rassérène au fond de mon regard",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "L’éternel crépuscule au sourire blafard :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Les couleurs cesseront d’offenser mon regard.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Déjà, se rassérène au fond de mon regard\nL’éternel crépuscule au sourire blafard :\nLes couleurs cesseront d’offenser mon regard."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "J’emporterai là-bas le souvenir des roses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et l’on effeuillera sur mes paupières closes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Les lilas et les lys, les roses et les roses.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "J’emporterai là-bas le souvenir des roses,\nEt l’on effeuillera sur mes paupières closes\nLes lilas et les lys, les roses et les roses."
